commit.message:
sparc.md (define_splits): Kill constraints.

2001-09-04  David S. Miller  <davem@redhat.com>

	* config/sparc/sparc.md (define_splits): Kill constraints.

From-SVN: r45370

files.patch:
@@ -1,3 +1,7 @@
+2001-09-04  David S. Miller  <davem@redhat.com>
+
+	* config/sparc/sparc.md (define_splits): Kill constraints.
+
 2001-09-03  Jakub Jelinek  <jakub@redhat.com>
 
 	* loop.c (express_from_1): Fix CONSTANT_P(a) case.

 (define_split

 	(match_operator:SI 2 "noov_compare_op"
 			   [(match_operand 1 "icc_or_fcc_reg_operand" "")
 			    (const_int 0)]))]

-				[(match_operand 2 "icc_or_fcc_reg_operand" "X,X")
+				[(match_operand 2 "icc_or_fcc_reg_operand" "")
 				 (const_int 0)])
-                         (match_operand:TF 3 "register_operand" "e,0")
-                         (match_operand:TF 4 "register_operand" "0,e")))]
+                         (match_operand:TF 3 "register_operand" "")
+                         (match_operand:TF 4 "register_operand" "")))]
   "reload_completed && TARGET_V9 && TARGET_FPU && !TARGET_HARD_QUAD"
   [(clobber (const_int 0))]
   "

 }")
